title: Accident on Hill Road
subTitle: Sonam's night of celebration turns into a disaster when her car hits an innocent man. Afraid of being punished for the crime, she decides to hide him but invites trouble in turn.

title: Thodi Thodi Si Manmaaniyan
subTitle: Raised by his mother alone, Siddharth dreams of settling in a foreign country. As part of a rock band, Siddharth enters a competition that changes his life.

title: Kya Yehi Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Rahul falls in love with Sandhya, a fellow college student, but realises that she does not reciprocate his feelings. Undeterred by her rejection, he still pursues her but pays a huge price for it.

title: Deewana Tere Naam Ka
subTitle: Friends Shankar and Shambhu share a lot in common and also end up falling in love with the same girl. However, when the girl loves Shankar, Shambhu parts ways with him and joins his rival.

title: Ab Kya Hoga
subTitle: A young man stumbles upon a mysterious woman, who he suspects of being a ghost. However, his worst fears come true when his mother arranges his marriage with the same woman.

title: Dil Ka Rishta
subTitle: Jai, a wealthy businessman in love with Tia, accidentally kills her husband in a car crash. After the accident Tia loses her memory and falls for Jai, who struggles with guilt.

title: Chirag
subTitle: When Asha is unable to conceive and loses her eyesight, her mother-in-law throws her out of the house and arranges for her son to remarry.

title: Swarag Se Sunder
subTitle: Two brothers struggle to keep their family together as external forces like the younger brother's father-in-law try to break them apart.

title: Rickshawala
subTitle: Gopi, a humble rickshaw puller, faces love and social prejudice as he pursues a relationship with Kiran, a woman from a higher class, challenging societal norms and personal conflicts.

title: I Proud to Be an Indian
subTitle: I, a man from India, travels to London for a family wedding and finds that their community is being threatened by a racist group. Seeing this, he decides to get involved and fight back.

title: Vidhaata
subTitle: After the death of his parent, Kunal lives with his grandfather Shamsher. However, when he falls in love with Durga, Shamsher plans to separate them.

title: Vidhaata
subTitle: After the death of his parent, Kunal lives with his grandfather Shamsher. However, when he falls in love with Durga, Shamsher plans to separate them.

title: Dil Kya Kare
subTitle: The parents of an adopted child face issues of love, betrayal and custody when their daughter's birth mother arrives.

title: Badlapur Boys
subTitle: Vijay grows up with a dream of bringing water to his village after his father's sacrifice goes in vain. So, he participates in a kabaddi tournament to attract the attention of the bureaucracy.

title: Be-Shaque
subTitle: Prakash goes to a village to look for his friend Shyam, who is missing. However, when he sees a picture of his lover, Roopa, with a man and a child, he gets baffled and decides to investigate.

title: Yudh
subTitle: A policeman sacrifices his life protecting Savitri and her twins from a gangster. Savitri raises the fallen officer's son as her twins, now separated, grow into a lawyer and a sniper.

title: Sharafat Gayi Tel Lene
subTitle: When an ordinary man discovers crores in his account, he is thrown into a tangled mess of crime, impersonation and corrupt connections he never asked for.

title: Mohabbat
subTitle: When Shekhar falls for Roopa, he approaches her father with his parents. However, when his stepmother asks Roopa's father for dowry, he vows to marry his daughter elsewhere.

title: Rishtey
subTitle: A man marries his lover and has a child with her against the wishes of her wealthy father. However, his scheming father-in-law ruins their marriage and leaves to care for his boy by himself.

title: Desi Tadka
subTitle: The newest compilation of preppy Punjabi music is played continuously for the viewers with a preference for Indian dance beats.

title: Amba
subTitle: When Amba gets her son Rajendra arrested for sexually assaulting their servant's daughter, Rajendra's wife wreaks havoc into their lives as she vows to avenge him.

title: Benaam Badsha
subTitle: An abandoned child shaped by violence grows into a feared criminal until a brave woman attempts to transform his brutal path through empathy and unwavering resolve.

title: Raj Kumar
subTitle: Rajkumar's mother sets out to oppose his marriage after she finds out that he plans to marry the rival kingdom's princess.

title: Raj Kumar
subTitle: Rajkumar's mother sets out to oppose his marriage after she finds out that he plans to marry the rival kingdom's princess.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Ram Avtar
subTitle: Childhood friends Ram and Avtar face a love triangle when Ram falls for Sangeeta, whom Avtar also loves. Ram sacrifices his love for Avtar, but their enemy Gundappaswami threatens to expose the truth.

title: Inteqam
subTitle: When Birju's sister, Chhaya, is raped and the court fails to mete out justice, his parents die due to the shock. Birju sets out to seek revenge and kidnaps Dinanath's sister.

title: Karamdaata
subTitle: Pinky, the granddaughter of a wealthy industrialist, runs away and marries a taxi driver. However, the businessman holds Pinky's lover responsible and gets him arrested.

title: Laila
subTitle: Deshraj and Leela's love thrives under the shadows of enmity between two Rajput families. This triggers a clash of expectations, egos, and bullets, placing several lives in danger.

title: Ek Chitthi Pyar Bhari
subTitle: A doctor puts out a job posting to recruit a nurse for his clinics in rural India. Unaware of a candidate's dark past, he hires her and eventually falls in love with her.

title: Raja Saab
subTitle: Upon Prince Pratap's insistence, Rajoo impersonates him in front of Princess Poonam. But the imitation lands him in trouble when she starts falling for Rajoo, unaware of his poor background.

title: Aan Baan
subTitle: Raja Bahadur indulges in various unlawful activities and is always saved by his brother, Suraj. When he decides to marry Rekha, Suraj, who is also in love with her, falls into a dilemma.

title: Har Dil Jo Pyar Karega
subTitle: Raj, an aspiring singer, rescues Pooja, the daughter of a wealthy man, from an accident. However, he soon finds himself in a web of complications when he falls in love with her best friend.

title: Joshila
subTitle: A jailor's daughter falls for a prisoner poet, believing him wrongly convicted and strives to prove his innocence and secure his release.
